summary: Replaces the male feet with a better model. Also replaces open-toed boots/shoes that show toes.
descriptionHtml:
Ever notice how the people of Skyrim have club feet? Me neither, but once you see it you can\'t help but notice. This little replacer gives men toes to run barefoot through Skyrim\'s snows, grip onto Skyrim\'s rocks and be stepped on by Skyrim\'s dragons. It also alters the open-toed shoes to use the new foot model. 

[b]N.B.: THIS MOD WILL BE UNNEEDED IF YOU ARE ALREADY USING A BODY REPLACER.[/b]


Big thanks to 4uDIK for the foot mesh from his [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6667]Real Body[/url]. Texture-wise the mod uses XCE\'s gritty/dirty skin for the body, 4uDIK\'s texture and normal for the foot and Bethseda\'s high-resolution normal map for the body.
author: MagicNakor
